{
  "texts": [
    "The new tensor is re-used as an input (now without a prompt) and a new, less noisy, tensor is determined.",
    "This process repeats for a fixed number of steps, whereby the final and least noisy tensor is decoded into an image.",
    "As the step from a latent space to a less noisy space is a simple operation for a GPU to perform (i.e.",
    "a subtraction of two tensors), the generation process is fast.",
    "Additionally, with sufficient iterations, the generated image contains negligible noise and is thus of high quality."
  ]
}